    dc:description "Figures 9–16. Aculops brevifolis sp. nov., female. 9. Antero-dorsal mite. 10. Coxal-genital region (Note: the coverflap of female flipped up). 11.Antero-lateral view. 12. Empodium (enlarged).13. Lateral opisthosoma (enlarged). 14. Postero-dorsal mite. 15. Genital region of male. 16. Leg I (enlarged). Scale bars: 9–11, 15–16=10μm." ;
